## Conditional Blocks

Templates use `{{#if VARIABLE}}...{{/if}}` for conditional sections:
```markdown
{{#if TELEGRAM_ENABLED}}
### Telegram Setup
Configure your Telegram bot token and chat ID here.
{{/if}}

{{#if EMAIL_ENABLED}}
### Email Setup
Configure your Gmail or Outlook credentials here.
{{/if}}
```

